OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry and rather cloudy
OL,6,Fwith the chance of the odd light
OL,7,Fshower across the west. Some sunny
OL,8,Fspells breaking through this
OL,9,Fafternoon, especially in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly dry this evening
OL,12,Falthough a little rain spreading to
OL,13,Fnorthern Argyll later. Then the rest
OL,14,Fof the night will be cloudy with
OL,15,Foccasional rain extending south.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FPatchy rain at first.
OL,18,FOtherwise dry and rather cloudy, some
OL,19,Fhazy sunshine developing in the
OL,20,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
