OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,7,Fsoutheast on Saturday, drier with a
OL,8,Ffew showers later. Mainly dry with
OL,9,Fjust the odd shower on Sunday. Chance
OL,10,Fof some rain on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
